  "detailed_description": "You are a penguin who has unexpectedly fallen into a crevasse.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse the keys W, A, S, D to move and the mouse to aim and fire your grappling hook.<br />\r\nUse Q and E to adjust the length of your grappling hook.<br />\r\n1,2 and F to use items.<br />\r\nWith practice, you'll be able to find quick moves and shortcuts.<br />\r\nBeware of moving platforms, slippery ice platforms and other obstacles.<br />\r\nCan you reach the top of the crevasse?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere's also an easy mode for those who don't like challenges, so even beginners can take on the challenge.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGood luck, everyone!",
  "about_the_game": "You are a penguin who has unexpectedly fallen into a crevasse.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse the keys W, A, S, D to move and the mouse to aim and fire your grappling hook.<br />\r\nUse Q and E to adjust the length of your grappling hook.<br />\r\n1,2 and F to use items.<br />\r\nWith practice, you'll be able to find quick moves and shortcuts.<br />\r\nBeware of moving platforms, slippery ice platforms and other obstacles.<br />\r\nCan you reach the top of the crevasse?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere's also an easy mode for those who don't like challenges, so even beginners can take on the challenge.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGood luck, everyone!",
